Done — I fixed the agent-status test path.

I updated `pulsar-rest/.../Models.kt` so REST `CommandStatus` uses REST-safe agent DTOs (`agentHistory`/`agentState`) instead of raw `AgentState`, and it now synthesizes a fallback state when an agent run finishes with only a final summary and no recorded action steps.

I kept the async E2E polling test in `CommandControllerE2ETest.kt` and added `CommandStatusJacksonSerializationTest.kt` to lock the JSON shape.

